---
// How It Works Section Component
---

<section id="how-it-works" class="how-it-works">
  <div class="container">
    <div class="section-header">
      <span class="label">Processo Simplificado</span>
      <h2>Como enviamos sua carga</h2>
    </div>

    <div class="steps-grid">
      <div class="line-connector"></div>

      <!-- Step 1 -->
      <div class="step">
        <div class="step-icon">
          <span class="material-symbols-outlined">request_quote</span>
        </div>
        <h3>1. Cotação</h3>
        <p>Solicite um orçamento online em segundos com base no peso e destino.</p>
      </div>

      <!-- Step 2 -->
      <div class="step">
        <div class="step-icon">
          <span class="material-symbols-outlined">package_2</span>
        </div>
        <h3>2. Coleta</h3>
        <p>Nossa equipe realiza a coleta da mercadoria no local agendado.</p>
      </div>

      <!-- Step 3 -->
      <div class="step">
        <div class="step-icon">
          <span class="material-symbols-outlined">location_on</span>
        </div>
        <h3>3. Rastreio</h3>
        <p>Acompanhe o trajeto da sua carga em tempo real através do nosso sistema.</p>
      </div>

      <!-- Step 4 -->
      <div class="step">
        <div class="step-icon final">
          <span class="material-symbols-outlined">check_circle</span>
        </div>
        <h3>4. Entrega</h3>
        <p>Entrega finalizada com segurança e confirmação digital de recebimento.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<style>
  .how-it-works {
    width: 100%;
    padding: var(--space-20) 0;
    background-color: var(--white);
    border-top: 1px solid var(--border-light);
    border-bottom: 1px solid var(--border-light);
  }

  .dark .how-it-works {
    background-color: var(--surface-dark);
    border-top-color: var(--border-dark);
    border-bottom-color: var(--border-dark);
  }

  .container {
    max-width: var(--container-max-width);
    margin: 0 auto;
    padding: 0 var(--space-4);
  }

  @media (min-width: 768px) {
    .container {
      padding-left: var(--container-padding-tablet);
      padding-right: var(--container-padding-tablet);
    }
  }

  @media (min-width: 1024px) {
    .container {
      padding-left: var(--container-padding-desktop);
      padding-right: var(--container-padding-desktop);
    }
  }

  .section-header {
    text-align: center;
    max-width: 48rem;
    margin: 0 auto var(--space-16);
  }

  .label {
    color: var(--primary);
    font-weight: var(--font-bold);
    text-transform: uppercase;
    letter-spacing: var(--tracking-wider);
    font-size: var(--text-sm);
  }

  h2 {
    font-size: var(--text-3xl);
    font-weight: var(--font-bold);
    color: var(--text-primary-light);
    margin-top: var(--space-2);
  }

  @media (min-width: 768px) {
    h2 {
      font-size: var(--text-4xl);
    }
  }

  .dark h2 {
    color: var(--white);
  }

  .steps-grid {
    position: relative;
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 1fr;
    gap: var(--space-8);
  }

  @media (min-width: 768px) {
    .steps-grid {
      grid-template-columns: repeat(4, 1fr);
    }
  }

  .line-connector {
    display: none;
  }

  @media (min-width: 768px) {
    .line-connector {
      display: block;
      position: absolute;
      top: 3rem;
      left: 0;
      width: 100%;
      height: 2px;
      background-color: var(--border-light);
      z-index: 0;
    }

    .dark .line-connector {
      background-color: var(--border-dark);
    }
  }

  .step {
    position: relative;
    z-index: 10;
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    align-items: center;
    text-align: center;
  }

  .step-icon {
    width: 6rem;
    height: 6rem;
    border-radius: var(--radius-full);
    background-color: var(--background-light);
    border: 4px solid var(--white);
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: center;
    margin-bottom: var(--space-6);
    box-shadow: var(--shadow-sm);
  }

  .dark .step-icon {
    background-color: var(--background-dark);
    border-color: var(--surface-dark);
  }

  .step-icon.final {
    background-color: var(--primary);
    border-color: var(--white);
    box-shadow: var(--shadow-lg), var(--shadow-primary);
  }

  .dark .step-icon.final {
    border-color: var(--surface-dark);
  }

  .step-icon .material-symbols-outlined {
    font-size: 36px;
    color: var(--text-primary-light);
  }

  .dark .step-icon .material-symbols-outlined {
    color: var(--primary);
  }

  .step-icon.final .material-symbols-outlined {
    color: var(--black);
  }

  h3 {
    font-size: var(--text-lg);
    font-weight: var(--font-bold);
    color: var(--text-primary-light);
    margin-bottom: var(--space-2);
  }

  .dark h3 {
    color: var(--white);
  }

  p {
    font-size: var(--text-sm);
    color: var(--text-secondary-light);
    line-height: var(--leading-normal);
  }

  .dark p {
    color: var(--text-tertiary-dark);
  }
</style>
